   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/9/-10

=head3 yQQQ (QQQ y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ತ್ರೈ 1 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ತ್ರೈ 4 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = ತ್ರೈ 3 -10

=head3 yQQQQ (QQQQ y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 1ನೇ ತ್ರೈಮಾಸಿಕ 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 4ನೇ ತ್ರೈಮಾಸಿಕ 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 3ನೇ ತ್ರೈಮಾಸಿಕ -10

=head3 yw-count-other ('week' w 'of' Y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = week 6 of 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = week 51 of 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = week 37 of -10
